@startuml architecture-overview-v2
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #374151
skinparam ArrowThickness 2

skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 14
  FontStyle bold
}

title LaunchLens v2 — Birds-Eye View (Parallel Execution)

' ── Swimlane layout ────────────────────────────────────────
|User|
:Paste product idea\nclick **Validate my idea**;

|#EEF2FF|Frontend (Next.js)|
:Show animated\n5-step progress bar\n+ elapsed timer;

|#FFF7ED|Backend (FastAPI)|
:Receive POST /launch;

' ── Pipeline stages ───────────────────────────────────────
|#F0FDF4|Agent 1 — Product Analyst|
:Read description\nExtract **3 customer profiles**\neach with search queries\nand pain intensity score;

|#FFF7ED|Backend (FastAPI)|
:Pass all 3 profiles\nto researcher simultaneously;

|#F0FDF4|Agent 2 — Community Researcher ⚡ PARALLEL|
fork
  :**Profile 1**\nSearch Reddit + HN\n(~3–5 tool calls);
fork again
  :**Profile 2**\nSearch Reddit + HN\n(~3–5 tool calls);
fork again
  :**Profile 3**\nSearch Reddit + HN\n(~3–5 tool calls);
end fork
:Merge: all 3 evidence sets ready;

|#FFF7ED|Backend (FastAPI)|
:Embed all posts\ninto shared vector store\n(one pass);

|#F0FDF4|Agent 3 — RAG Synthesizer ⚡ PARALLEL|
fork
  :**Profile 1**\nSemantic search\n+ LLM synthesis;
fork again
  :**Profile 2**\nSemantic search\n+ LLM synthesis;
fork again
  :**Profile 3**\nSemantic search\n+ LLM synthesis;
end fork
:Merge: 3 SynthesisResults ready;

|#F0FDF4|Agent 4 — PMF Scorer|
:Score market demand **1–10**\nwith chain-of-thought reasoning\nTag: strongest signal · biggest gap\nVerdict: strong / moderate /\nweak / insufficient;

|#FFF7ED|Backend (FastAPI)|
if (Verdict strong\nor moderate?) then (yes)
  :Route to\nAgent 5;
else (no → weak signal)
  :Skip copy\nAssemble early report;
endif

|#F0FDF4|Agent 5 — GTM Copywriter ⚡ PARALLEL|
fork
  :Cold outreach\nmessage;
fork again
  :Reddit post\nangle;
fork again
  :Landing page\nheadline + sub;
end fork
:Merge: GTMPack ready;

|#FFF7ED|Backend (FastAPI)|
:Assemble **LaunchLensReport**\nReturn JSON to frontend;

|#EEF2FF|Frontend (Next.js)|
:Render tabbed report:\n**Overview** (score · signal · gap)\n**Audience** (ICP persona cards)\n**Launch Copy** (copy buttons);

|User|
:Read score · evidence · copy\nLaunch or pivot;

@enduml
